Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Rudolph Giuliani's New York
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yktry
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 24 Mar 1995
School dinners, gangsters, snow ploughs and the other problems faced by the Mayor of New York City, Rudolph Giuliani, are explored by Alistair Cooke.